      "text": "#include <iostream>\nusing namespace std;\n\nint main() {\n    int n;\n    cin >> n;\n\n    for (int i = 1; i <= 10; i++) {\n        cout << n << \" x \" << i << \" = \" << n * i << endl;\n    }\n\n    return 0;\n}\n",
